knocked out of place.

17:27.414 --> 17:28.780
Not too sure.

17:28.782 --> 17:31.215
- Well there's a garage
not far from here.

17:31.217 --> 17:34.085
I could call you a
tow, if you want me to.

17:34.087 --> 17:37.321
- Yeah, I can
