23:58.671 --> 24:00.571
Because he's a liar.

24:01.673 --> 24:03.941
Oh, come on, he's a nice guy.

24:03.943 --> 24:05.443
Not he's not.

24:05.445 --> 24:10.581
Everything he's said since
he's got here has been a lie.

24:10.583 --> 24:11.682
Really?

24:15.821 --> 24:17.855
For starters, there's the fact

24:17.857 --> 24:20.691
that he doesn't even like girls.

24:20.693 --> 24:21.792
What?

24:22.794 --> 24:24.628
He's basically gay.

24:24.630 --> 24:27.765
He doesn't get hard with girls.

24:27.767 --> 24:31.802
- That's a really strange thing
to say about your brother.

24:31.804 --> 24:34.805
- And then, I guess
there's the fact

24:34.807 --> 24:38.242
that he's taking
advantage of you.

24:38.244 --> 24:41.078
I mean honestly, he
thinks your an idiot.

24:41.080 --> 24:43.514
You'll do whatever he wants.

24:43.516 --> 24:46.951
Well really, you don't
even know who he is.

24:56.027 --> 24:58.262
Actually, I was wondering.

25:00.599 --> 25:04.768
When you work out here,
in the middle of nowhere,

25:06.171 --> 25:09.106
