or a murderer or something?

25:21.653 --> 25:23.787
And how can you tell
that isn't gonna like,

25:23.789 --> 25:26.524
rape you or kill you or rob you,

25:29.628 --> 25:32.930
or has that never even
crossed your mind?

25:34.065 --> 25:36.834
If I were you, it
definitely would.

25:38.203 --> 25:41.705
