met a guy like him,

25:41.707 --> 25:43.674
I'd probably like, run.

26:02.827 --> 26:04.128
Where were you?

26:26.651 --> 26:28.719
What did you say to her?

26:30.822 --> 26:33.591
She's really an idiot.

26:33.593 --> 26:34.625
